ch.nolix.core.container

Class ReadContainer<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.nolix.core.container.ReadContainer<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type of the elements of a read container.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IContainer<E>, java.lang.Iterable<E>

    public final class ReadContainer<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IContainer<E>
    A read container provides methods to read on a given container. A read container prevents that its accessed container can be mutated, but not that the elements of its accessed container can be mutated.
    Author:
    Silvan Wyss
